title: 01/06/22 DPS Hour 2 Chris Mannix and Ross Tucker

description:
Chris Mannix talks to Dan about Zion and his rehab. Chris says that Ben Simmons plays before Zion. Ross Tucker talks to Dan about Antonio Brown and the possible way that he can play again for another team.
